text: Tesa Vilar (born 3 September 1995) is a former Slovenian professional racing cyclist. She rode for the BTC City Ljubljana team in the 2015 cycling season. ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
